Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:33.45,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you seem to have guts. I like that about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:35.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Yukito-san is a very good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:39.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let him stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:40.19,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:42.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? Of course! I'm deadly serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:44.67,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are two conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:45.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll sleep in the shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:47.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You will have a drink with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:56.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, in the end, this is what he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.91,0:10:00.82,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Perhaps the one who fell in love was me."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:02.23,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.23,0:10:03.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:04.75,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I win, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I told him,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:09.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"The fish you let escape was a mermaid,"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:10.97,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.97,0:10:12.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That struck home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.89,0:10:14.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it end up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:16.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy's at her best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:19.31,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, freeloader. Why are you looking so glum?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:21.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:22.35,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My eeeeeyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:23.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.58,0:10:26.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:31.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything, like a story of an erotic confession of love or a hidden talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:32.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:33.66,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:38.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's the doll from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:45.49,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:48.46,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This trick is how I earn a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.81,0:10:51.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother also used to travel with this as her profession.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:54.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does this have a punch line?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:59.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No good. You're not funny at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:03.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't it amazing he's not using any tricks?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.01,0:11:04.89,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.89,0:11:08.85,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it had obvious strings showing, it would be better if it were funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:09.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.09,0:11:12.98,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! He's leaving on his own!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:16.33,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't really matter that you don't have any talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:18.09,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just down the sorrow with some drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:22.02,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Haruko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:23.62,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruko Kamio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:25.58,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me one more glass, missus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:29.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you my name so that you wouldn't call me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:31.88,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! You're such an insensitive guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:35.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.34,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a runaway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:38.17,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:41.83,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you chasing a goal or a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:42.80,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:44.76,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:46.38,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, compared to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:51.69,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite a funny guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:52.42,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:55.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look like it, but I have a pretty good eye for judging men.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:57.57,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can let you stay for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:11:59.28,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:02.40,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you look after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:03.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:06.92,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've seen her reckless side, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:11.08,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's impulsive, and once something catches her eye, she'll be attracted to it like a bee to honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.30,0:12:12.65,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm a babysitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:16.54,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, can you stop her saying that phrase?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:17.93,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gao!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:21.01,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what she says when she's frustrated or about to cry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:22.10,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:24.84,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's supposed to sound like a dinosaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:29.47,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She loves dinosaurs. She's been saying that since she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:32.86,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's still just a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:45.05,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.06,0:12:47.53,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have to take remedial classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:49.99,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Haruko already left?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.99,0:12:52.50,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She leaves early every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:55.44,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the first time in a while that I've eaten breakfast with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:58.91,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukito-san, what are you going to do today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.91,0:13:01.18,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I'll walk you to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:06.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruko asked me to watch you so that you don't do anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:09.81,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She still doesn't trust me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.37,0:13:11.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gao~!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:13.30,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:14.52,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a map of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.95,0:13:16.27,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:19.79,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It will show you where you people gather together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:22.07,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be useful for your work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:24.72,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:27.61,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:29.22,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-chin is in a pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:35.25,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come to pick you up after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:36.55,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll meet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:37.36,Air Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
